msgid "Sensitivity"
msgstr "Sensibilitat"

#: sensitivity.ui:12
msgid "Show panel when mouse approaches edge of the screen"
msgstr "Mostra la barra quan el ratolí s'apropi a la vora de la pantalla."

#: sensitivity.ui:13
msgid ""
"When enabled, show panel not only in overview but also when the mouse "
"approaches the edge of the screen"
msgstr ""

