msgid ""
"When enabled, also show panel when mouse approaches edge of the screen when "
"windows are in fullscreen mode"
msgstr ""

#: sensitivity.ui:24
msgid "Show panel in overview"
msgstr "Mostra la barra a la vista general."

#: sensitivity.ui:25
msgid "When enabled, the panel will be visible in overview"
msgstr ""

#: sensitivity.ui:30
msgid "Keep hot corner sensitive, even in hidden state"
msgstr "Mantén el cantó actiu sensible, fins i tot en mode ocult."

#: sensitivity.ui:31
msgid ""
"When enabled, keeps the hot corner sensitive even when panel is in hidden"
msgstr ""

#: sensitivity.ui:36
msgid "Show overview when mouse approaches edge of the screen"
msgstr ""

#: sensitivity.ui:37
msgid ""
"When enabled, the panel and overview are both shown when the mouse "
"approaches the edge of the screen"
msgstr ""

#: sensitivity.ui:42
msgid "Keep round corners when top bar is hidden"
msgstr "Mantén els cantons arrodonits quan la barra estigui oculta."

#: sensitivity.ui:43
msgid ""
"When enabled, keep the round corners on the top even when the panel is hidden"
msgstr ""

